703955f-a.title: Brooklyn: Degraw Street - Tompkins Place
703955f-a.text:
2492253 Degraw Street, between Tompkins Place and Court Street. A
view of an old frame house in existence prior to 1880, and still standing in
(1929). Next to it is the Trinity Evang. Lutheran Church.
October 1928.
Hugene L. Armbruster Collection.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
